Yume ou tame ni

550
00:44:35,400 --> 00:44:41,600
Tabi ni deta hazu sa

551
00:44:41,600 --> 00:44:48,600
Tôi natsu no ano hi

552
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:55,500
Ashita sae mieta nara

